description:
The Nazis, masters of the world and space?!

End of 1943, the Reich has beaten the USSR and now stretches from the Atlantic to Vladivostok. In the summer of 1945, America wishes to boost its image and challenge the Reich by deciding to send a craft into space.

But it faces two great adversaries: Werner von Braun, whose missiles destroyed Moscow, and Hitler, who despises the Americans. All the power of the Reich is launched into the battle with the crazy aim of installing one day nothing less than a German base on the Moon!
name: Duel d'aigles
